                  </persName>
            ." There is also the name of Mr. Mappel. I recollect Vincent; I am sure she is the person.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18160529-45-person431">
                  JOHN 
                  MAPPEL
               <interp inst="t18160529-45-person431" type="surname" value="MAPPEL"></interp>
