                     <interp inst="t18160529-45-person442" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was a mark woman.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18160529-45-person443">
                  Elizabeth 
                  Coward
               <interp inst="t18160529-45-person443" type="surname" value="Coward"></interp>
